    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="question">
                <p>Do you think it is more important to have an enjoyable job or to make money? Explain your point of view.</p>
                <note type="word-limit">(at least 100 words)</note>
                <label type="level">
                    <span>B2</span>
                </label>
            </div>
            <div type="answer">
                <p>I think the most important is to feel happy with your work, whatever your salary.</p>
                <p/>
                <p>Why earn money if you feel miserable and depressed ?</p>
                <p/>
                <p>In my opinion, that isn't the recipe of the happiness.</p>
                <p/>
                <p>Money is just a sheet of paper with numbers onto it, it's just silly to think money is a goal. Money is just a tool which is important to build your project alone.</p>
                <p/>
                <p>You don't need money if you've a lot of friends because your friends can helps you too.</p>
                <p/>
                <p>If you want to earn a lot of money, you can try Monopoly with your friends.</p>
                <p/>
                <p>You'll preserve your health, your good mood and your friend.</p>
            </div>
